{"tid":1026427,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《叉燒包》原唱者、邵氏女星「噴火女郎」張仲文病逝，享年82歲","createTime":"2019-02-18T06:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T07:59:20.000Z","uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7a7621fafe4d5bca22039640002101be30b49bf0","tid":1026427,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"【RIP】《叉燒包》原唱者 邵氏女星張仲文病逝 享年82歲 (12:07)<br />\n2019/2/18<br />\n<br />\n張仲文在德州病逝，享年82歲。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190218/s00009/f39c4a1c0412b4e1c03bc5b5ae323f5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190218%2Fs00009%2Ff39c4a1c0412b4e1c03bc5b5ae323f5c.jpg&h=d6483776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n徐小鳳金曲《叉燒包》的原唱者，有「噴火女郎」之稱的邵氏女星張仲文，被指因器官衰竭在美國病逝，享年82歲。1936年8月出世的張仲文是河北省人，她是國語片著名性感女星，由於形象豪放又野性，故有「噴火女郎」稱號。據悉，張仲文在1954年入台灣中影演員訓練班，畢業後簽約為該公司的第一批基本演員，到1958年她獲亞洲影業公司青睞，演出《三姊妹》，並邊跳邊唱主題曲《叉燒包》，而該歌大受歡迎，及後徐小鳳都有翻唱。<br />\n<br />\n在1959年上映的《噴火女郎》，張仲文憑冶艷形象探入民心，及後她曾擔正演出電影《潘金蓮》，於1966年拍完《西遊記》後，嫁給一名德國人，漸漸離開娛樂圈。<br />\n<br />\n（即時娛樂）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190218/1550462650938/【rip】《叉燒包》原唱者-邵氏女星張仲文病逝-享年82歲\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190218%2F1550462650938%2F%E3%80%90rip%E3%80%91%E3%80%8A%E5%8F%89%E7%87%92%E5%8C%85%E3%80%8B%E5%8E%9F%E5%94%B1%E8%80%85-%E9%82%B5%E6%B0%8F%E5%A5%B3%E6%98%9F%E5%BC%B5%E4%BB%B2%E6%96%87%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D-%E4%BA%AB%E5%B9%B482%E6%AD%B2&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgFDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=611b4e2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190218%2F1550462650938%2F%E3%80%90rip%E3%80%91%E3%80%8A%E5%8F%89%E7%87%92%E5%8C%85%E3%80%8B%E5%8E%9F%E5%94%B1%E8%80%85-%E9%82%B5%E6%B0%8F%E5%A5%B3%E6%98%9F%E5%BC%B5%E4%BB%B2%E6%96%87%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D-%E4%BA%AB%E5%B9%B482%E6%AD%B2&h=74d8ffa6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/2